title: Taylor Swift & Charli XCX Team Up for 'Boom Clap' Duet in Toronto - Watch Now!
text: Taylor Swift and Charli XCX throw their hands up in the air while performing together at the 1989 World Tour show at Rogers Center on Saturday evening (October 3) in Toronto, Canada. The 25-year-old entertainer surprised the crowd with the 23-year-old British singer to sing her hit track “Boom Clap.” Watch their duet below! Taylor [...] »
